{"tid":1453770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪忘記左葉虎單野呀！！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T16:49:27.000Z","uid":301911,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2e4474334a369b7a2f8ddb9963cf50f4915522","tid":1453770,"uid":301911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"大家唔好唔記得葉虎單野！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n架車發現大量攻擊性武器、大陸軍帽、葉虎地址證明！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知道文宣組呢排好辛苦，但係文宣組可否繼續幫幫手！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e5d30d877480daefcc7f5faeeded1c3c7ae7e8","tid":1453770,"uid":301911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"869f065b12a2fdf642ca83a1f35e59ec041b1443","tid":1453770,"uid":301911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:18:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"38c4e6507836d95dd77f1dfca14debd4be6ab9fa","tid":1453770,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f100dda163e7c6580b1e45d4b9869ebf953367","tid":1453770,"uid":301911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:19:53.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b7c5f45d4ea68533f9e6f6d0c9a68968081e03cc","tid":1453770,"uid":154247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:2