<br />\n準備片<br />\nFollow up questions<br />\n如果係驅趕，佢哋已經喺地鐵站走緊！ 點解仲要放？ 如果係拘捕，你應該衝入去拉人而唔係放催淚彈胡椒彈！可唔可以解釋下<br />\n<strong>預設答案：</strong>情況混亂，個別事件<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n警察冇專業訓練處理混亂情況？<br />\n個別例子係合理解釋？殺人放火強姦都係個別例子！ 示威者都係混亂情況下先做出唔尋常，唔理智行為，警方接唔接受呢個解釋唔落charge？<br />\n<br />\n5. 有片影到警察放武器入示威者背囊，點解？係唔係插贓嫁禍？<br />\n<strong>預設答案&nbsp;：</strong>&nbsp;冇資料<br />\n預備嗰條片， 講埋時間地點<br />\n叫佢解釋！<br />\n<br />\n6. 太古零距離開槍， 做法是否恰當？咩原因同情況下要咁做？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n7. 北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者， 荃灣白衣人 一離場，場警察就進場，又係一個巧合？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n8. 頭部嚴重受傷，明顯見到一灘血喺地面，已被制服，完全冇反抗能力，哭求唔好撳， 點解仲要惡意跪喺個頭上面？ 因為仇恨？因為唔識聽廣東話？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/703181869/posts/10157404127116870?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F703181869%2Fposts%2F10157404127116870%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=f2540e6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/703181869/posts/10157404127116870?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n問呢條嘅目的係煽情，同埋尋日條片畀cctvb剪咗<br />\n<br />\n一齊畀意見！！<br />\n葵芳地鐵站內放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchishing87%2Fvideos%2F10156292523426674%2F&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=5cd4f673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/</a><br />\n<br />\n追打並推落扶手電梯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196364073824126&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=617da9c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126</a><br />\n<br />\n太古站開槍 1米內射示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424996360930416&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=fcb4c097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416</a><br />\n<br />\n竹支嫁禍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424974427599276&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=b25ee146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276</a><br />\n<br />\n唔回應是否扮示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196515767142290&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=20e73365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者會共識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449180</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n求大家將呢段散去所以唔同post，代推文<br />\n<br />\n一定要畀記者知<br />\n佢哋係我哋唯一嘅槍口，可以直接質問黑警同政府"},{"pid":"9c721647a69ba229988928bcbed29ef9aeeba566","tid":1453770,"uid":223295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d1e39a3c8617d9a3c0bac8a5ea041068332295","tid":1453770,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:58.000Z","msg":"咁你想點呀？<br />\n<br />\n係咪去西環？<br />\n<br />\n你講你認為要點做啦！"},{"pid":"f17dc9b6e4ac76596794b99e3bd747082f868a7c","tid":1453770,"uid":210895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已